</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1051,1155,1207]" pageId="34" pageNumber="1179">
E t y m o l o g y: The specific epithet, 
<emphasis box="[585,668,1155,1176]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="1179">hadrosa</emphasis>
is a Greek name that stems from &quot;hodros&quot; (= well developed); with reference to the well-developed phallobasic loop.
</paragraph>
